3. ADD A TOMCAT USER in /opt/tomcat9/conf/tomcat-users.xml 
   sudo vi /tomcat9/conf/tomcat-users.xml
but if already in tomcat9 then: sudo vi conf/tomcat-users.xml

   <user username="boss" password="admin123" roles="manager-gui,admin-gui,manager-script"/>
   <user username="blest" password="admin123" roles="admin-gui"/>

